OL,3,CEqualities watchdog issues interim
OL,4,Cguidance on single-sex spaces
OL,6,FThe equalities watchdog has issued
OL,7,Finterim guidance in the wake of the
OL,8,FSupreme Court ruling that the term
OL,9,Fwoman is defined by biological sex.
OL,11,FTrans women "should not be permitted
OL,12,Fto use the women's facilities" in
OL,13,Fworkplaces or public-facing services
OL,14,Flike shops and hospitals, the Equality
OL,15,Fand Human Rights Commission (EHRC)
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,18,FThe same applies to trans men, who are
OL,19,Fbiologically female, using men's
OL,20,Ftoilets.
