OL,6,FBut the watchdog also insisted that
OL,7,Ftrans people "should not be put in a
OL,8,Fposition where there are no facilities
OL,9,Ffor them to use".
OL,11,FOver the Easter period, the Supreme
OL,12,FCourt declared that the words "woman"
OL,13,Fand "sex" in the Equality Act refer to
OL,14,Fa biological woman and biological sex.
OL,16,FThe ruling has been interpreted to
OL,17,Fmean that trans women, who are
OL,18,Fbiologically male but identify as
OL,19,Fwomen, can be excluded from women-only
OL,20,Fspaces like toilets and changing rooms.
