OL,3,CEqualities watchdog issues interim
OL,4,Cguidance on single-sex spaces
OL,6,F"Suitable alternative provisions may
OL,7,Fbe required" for trans pupils, the
OL,8,Fwatchdog said, as trans girls "should
OL,9,Fnot be permitted to use the girls'
OL,10,Ftoilet or changing facilities, and
OL,11,Fpupils who identify as trans boys
OL,12,F(biological girls) should not be
OL,13,Fpermitted to use the boys' toilet or
OL,14,Fchanging facilities".
OL,16,FThe watchdog also said that sports
OL,17,Fclubs and other associations of 25 or
OL,18,Fmore people are allowed to be
OL,19,Fexclusively for biological men or
OL,20,Fwomen.
